{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/koe-no-katachi-silent-voice-kesempatan-kedua-dan-persahabatan/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Koe no Katachi (A Silent Voice): Kesempatan Kedua dan Persahabatan","content":"<p>Bro sis, udah pada nonton Koe no Katachi belum?</p>\n<p>Anime ini diangkat dari manga yang berjudul sama, Koe no Katachi. Manga nya sendiri ada tujuh volume. Kalo yang udah khatam sama manga nya nih, kira-kira cukup nggak yah untuk dijadikan satu film aja? Ternyata Kyoto Animation cukup total menggarap adaptasinya. Mereka mengadaptasi <em>manga</em> tersebut menjadi film yang berdurasi 130 menit, atau setara dengan 2 jam 10 menit.</p>\n<p>Film ini berkisah mengenai Ishida Shouya, yang hidupnya berubah seratus delapan puluh derajat sejak ia mem-<em>bully</em> Nishimiya Shouko, murid pindahan tuna rungu di SD-nya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_4624\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4624\" data-attachment-id=\"4624\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/koe-no-katachi-silent-voice-kesempatan-kedua-dan-persahabatan/attachment/1-10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/1-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Cover Koe no Katachi versi manga\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Cover Koe no Katachi versi manga (myanimelist.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/1-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/1-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4624\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/1-2.jpg\" alt=\"Cover Koe no Katachi versi manga (myanimelist.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-4624\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Cover Koe no Katachi versi manga (myanimelist.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Setelah Nishimiya pindah sekolah akibat tidak tahan di-<em>bully</em>, Shouya justru menjadi objek <em>bully</em> teman-temannya, membuat kepribadiannya berubah dari ceria menjadi canggung dan pemurung.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_4627\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4627\" data-attachment-id=\"4627\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/koe-no-katachi-silent-voice-kesempatan-kedua-dan-persahabatan/attachment/2-10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/2-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"New student\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;New student (mangathering.wordpress.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/2-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/2-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4627\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/2-2.jpg\" alt=\"New student (mangathering.wordpress.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-4627\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">New student (mangathering.wordpress.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Memasuki dunia SMA, Shouya yang masih dibayang-bayangi oleh perilakunya di masa lalu mencoba menemui Nishimiya untuk menebus kesalahannya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_4630\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4630\" data-attachment-id=\"4630\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/koe-no-katachi-silent-voice-kesempatan-kedua-dan-persahabatan/attachment/3-10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/3-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Social anxiety in a nutshell\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Social anxiety in a nutshell (niusnews.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/3-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/3-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4630\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/3-2.jpg\" alt=\"Social anxiety in a nutshell (niusnews.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-4630\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Social anxiety in a nutshell (niusnews.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Karena telah membaca manganya terlebih dahulu, plot dan alur ceritanya terasa familiar bagi saya. Memang film ini sangat setia pada sumber aslinya, terutama di bagian awal film. Ini juga yang bisa membuat beberapa penonton merasa <em>pace</em> dari anime ini agak lambat, apalagi jika dibandingkan dengan beberapa anime yang bukan hasil adaptasi.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_4633\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4633\" data-attachment-id=\"4633\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/koe-no-katachi-silent-voice-kesempatan-kedua-dan-persahabatan/attachment/4-8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/4-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Teasing gone too far\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Teasing gone too far (thehypedgeek.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/4-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/4-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4633\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/4-2.jpg\" alt=\"Teasing gone too far (thehypedgeek.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-4633\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Teasing gone too far (thehypedgeek.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Di lain pihak, mungkin karena keterbatasan waktu, ada beberapa bagian plot yang dihilangkan, padahal menurut saya justru bagian yang dihilangkan tersebut cukup penting terhadap dinamika hubungan Shouya dengan Shouko dan karakter lainnya. Tetapi secara keseluruhan, inti cerita Koe no Katachi sudah tersampaikan dengan baik.<br />\nDesain karakter anime ini juga mengikuti desain karakter manganya. Pengisi suaranya oke, saya terkesan dengan pengisi suara Shouko. Sementara itu, animasi latar belakangnya cukup enak dilihat, walaupun belum sekelas Makoto Shinkai atau Mamoru Hosoda. <em>Background</em> musik untuk film ini pun terasa pas dengan tema filmnya. Selain tema penebusan dosa dan persahabatan, Koe no Katachi juga memaparkan pentingnya komunikasi dalam menjembatani perbedaan, melalui cerita yang mengalir dan menyentuh hati. <em>Overall</em>, anime ini sangat saya rekomendasikan untuk ditonton.</p>\n<p>Berikut trailernya:</p>\n<p><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe class='youtube-player' type='text/html' width='1280' height='720' src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ivrq1ZwsRps?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;autohide=2&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;wmode=transparent' allowfullscreen='true' style='border:0;'></iframe></span></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"54abf84f-d38a-50b2-baf0-90974645bb86"}}}